# Custom Ch3 Memo
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.paperSpriteFolderName=The folder to use for the paper sprites. Leave empty to use the vanilla paper sprites.\nTo make your own, copy Graphics/Atlases/Memo from the graphics dump to your mod, in Graphics/Atlases/MaxHelpingHandCustomMemos/MyUniqueFolderName, and type "MyUniqueFolderName" here.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.dialogId=The ID of the dialog to use for the text the memo will display.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.dialogBeforeId=The ID of the dialog to display before seeing the memo.\nLeave empty if you do not want any dialogue before the memo.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.dialogAfterId=The ID of the dialog to display after seeing the memo.\nLeave empty if you do not want any dialogue after the memo.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.flagOnCompletion=If specified, the given session flag will be activated once the memo cutscene is over.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.dialogBeforeOnlyOnce=If enabled, the dialog before the memo will only display when interacting with the memo for the first time in the session.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CustomCh3Memo.tooltips.dialogAfterOnlyOnce=If enabled, the dialog after the memo will only display when interacting with the memo for the first time in the session.

