placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/PopStrawberrySeedsTrigger.tooltips.popMultiRoomStrawberrySeeds=Whether Multi-Room Strawberry Seeds (from max480's Helping Hand) should pop as well while the player is in the trigger.

