placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/SetCustomInventoryTrigger.tooltips.backpack=Whether the player has a backpack or not.
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/SetCustomInventoryTrigger.tooltips.groundRefills=Whether the player gets a refill upon touching the ground.

# Reskinnable Touch Switch
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableTouchSwitch.tooltips.icon=The name of the icon for the touch switch.\nTo make your own, place your frames in Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/myfolder/iconXX.png, then type "myfolder/icon" here.\nThe vanilla icon frames can be found in the graphics dump, at Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/objects/touchswitch/iconXX.png.
