placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableTouchSwitch.tooltips.inactiveColor=The switch color when not triggered yet.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableTouchSwitch.tooltips.activeColor=The switch color when triggered, but the group is not complete yet.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableTouchSwitch.tooltips.finishColor=The switch color when the group is complete.

