placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableSwitchGate.tooltips.persistent=Will stay open once activated, even if the player dies.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableSwitchGate.tooltips.sprite=Changes the visual appearance of the switch gate.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/ReskinnableSwitchGate.tooltips.icon=The name of the icon for the switch gate.\nTo make your own, place your frames in Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/myfolder/iconXX.png, then type "myfolder/icon" here.\nThe vanilla icon frames can be found in the graphics dump, at Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/objects/switchgate/iconXX.png.
